          </identifier>
          <title>
            <string language="en">Actin-myosin Crossbridge Animation</string>
            <string language="x-mt-de">Actin-Myosin Crossbridge Animation</string>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">Animation de Crossbridge d'Actine-myosine</string>
            <string language="x-mt-pt">Animation De Crossbridge Do Actin-Actin-myosin</string>
            <string language="x-mt-it">Animazione Di Crossbridge Della Actina-miosina</string>
            <string language="x-mt-el">Crossbridge ακτίνιο-μυοσην ζωτικότητα</string>
            <string language="x-mt-es">Animación De Crossbridge Del Actinia-Actin-myosin</string>
          </title>
          <description>
            <string language="en">Roger Sabbadini, Ph.D., was the motivation behind this animation. The actin-myosin crossbridge system is complex, and we are really only speculating on the details in many ways. However, if a picture is worth a thousand words, this one second, 15 frame, animation is worth at least 15 thousand.</string>
          </description>
          <keyword>
            <string language="en">Science and Technology</string>
          </keyword>
          <language>en</language>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-de">Roger Sabbadini, Ph.D., war der Beweggrund hinter 
dieser Animation. Das Actin-Myosin crossbridge System ist 
kompliziert, und wir spekulieren wirklich nur auf den Details in 
vielen Methoden. Jedoch wenn eine Abbildung tausend Wörter 
wertIST, gestalten diese eine Sekunde, 15, Animation wertIST 
mindestens 15 tausend.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">Roger Sabbadini, Ph.D., était la motivation 
derrière cette animation. Le système de crossbridge 
d'actine-myosine est complexe, et nous speculons vraiment seulement 
sur les détails de beaucoup de voies. Cependant, si une image 
vaut la peine mille mots, cette une seconde, 15 encadrent, animation 
vaut la peine au moins 15 mille.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-pt">Roger Sabbadini, Ph.D., era o motivation atrás 
deste animation. O sistema do crossbridge do actin-actin-myosin 
é complexo, e nós speculating realmente somente nos detalhes em 
muitas maneiras. Entretanto, se um retrato valer a pena mil 
palavras, este um segundo, 15 molda, animation vale a pena ao menos 15
mil.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-it">Roger Sabbadini, Ph.D., era la motivazione dietro 
questa animazione. Il sistema del crossbridge della 
actina-miosina è complesso e stiamo speculando realmente soltanto sui
particolari in molti modi. Tuttavia, se un'immagine vale mille 
parole, questo un secondo, 15 incornicia, animazione vale almeno 15 
mila.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-el">Ο Roger Sabbadini, ph. Δ., ήταν το κίνητρο 
πίσω από αυτήν την ζωτικότητα. Το crossbridge 
ακτίνιο-μυοσην σύστημα είναι σύνθετο, και πραγματικά μόνο 
σκεπτόμαστε στις λεπτομέρειες από πολλές απόψεις. 
Εντούτοις, εάν μια εικόνα αξίζει χίλιες λέξεις, αυτή 
δεύτερος, 15 πλαίσιο, ζωτικότητα αξίζει τουλάχιστον 15 
χιλιάδες.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-es">Roger Sabbadini, Ph.D., era la motivación detrás 
de esta animación. El sistema del crossbridge del 
actinia-actin-myosin es complejo, y estamos especulando realmente 
solamente sobre los detalles de muchas maneras. Sin embargo, si 
un cuadro vale mil palabras, este un segundo, 15 enmarca, animación 
vale por lo menos 15 miles.</string>
          </description>
          <keyword>
            <string language="x-mt-de">Wissenschaft und Technologie</string>
